                    {
                        "name": "Suck Blood",
                        "type": "offensive_action",
                        "text": "<b>Requirements</b> The flea swarm\u2019s last action was Swarming Bites, and it dealt damage to at least one enemy; <b>Effect</b> The flea swarm drinks the creatures\u2019 blood. Each victim becomes drained 1 and the swarm regains 3 HP for each victim drained.",
                        "action": {
