                        "name": "Swarming Bites",
                        "type": "offensive_action",
                        "text": "Each enemy in the swarm\u2019s space takes 2d4+7 piercing damage and must attempt a DC 22 basic Reflex save. A creature that fails its save is exposed to flea fever.",
